title: Battle At The Rat Bowl Trailer
description:
​Skateboarders from all over the World - you’ll better prepare yourself for the first annual „Battle At The Rat Bowl“ presented by Volcom !
Designed by no other but Volcom teamrider Rune Glifberg, the Rat Bowl, based at the Northbrigade Skatepark in Cologne, can simply be called one oft he radest pits in all over Germany.
Reason enough for Volcom to make it a call and celebrate the construction of this Monster.
The session will go down by the 4th of June so you better cancel all your appointments, minding that there is an overall cash purse of 6.000€ in the open division and lots of stuff prizes in all divisions (Pro/Am – Masters – Kids – Women – Best trick)

The registration will already start by the 3rd June at 16 pm and on the contest day from 9-11 am at the Northbrigade Skatepark.

Starting fee:

Open, Master & Women division – 15,00€

Kids division – 10,00€

The fee also icludes the entry to the riderslounge ( VIP area, Free Drinks & Bratwurst, Storage place ) and the free entry for the Aftershowparty / HOLY STOKES premiere)

All Afterparty/Premiere infos will follow.
9:00-11:00: Registration
11:00 Contest Start
